data.description: BEAUTIFUL HOME in Fabulous Lochmere at Forest Ridge! Grand Entry with Extensive Wood Floors throughout. Plantation Shutters on All Windows. Vaulted, Pretty Office. 5Beds/3.5 Baths. Oversized Family Room & Large Kitchen with Island & Instant Hot Water. Master Suite & 2nd Bed with Private Bath Down. Huge Game Room with wet bar + Media Room or 5th Bedroom up. 2 Tankless HWH. Storm Shelter. Sprinkler. Room for a pool! Golf, Ponds, Trails and so much more to offer!
